                    <h1 class="u-entryTitle">Mercury Astronaut Scott Carpenter and the Controversy Surrounding Aurora 7</h1>
          <p class="Article-excerpt">
  This past May, I went to Spacefest V in Tucson, Arizona, one of the few events where you’d do well...
</p>

<p class="Article-author">
                    By
                              <a href="https://www.popsci.com/authors/amy-shira-teitel/"
             rel="author"
             class="fn author-link">
            Amy Shira Teitel
          </a>
                
